Process and match function parameters

Source: R/targeter.R
process_parameters.Rd

This function validates and processes key parameters by matching them against their allowed values.

Arguments

binning_method

character - method for binning numeric variables

order_label

character - order method for labels in output

target_type

character - type of the target variable

woe_alternate_version

character - when to use alternate WOE definition

useNA

character - how to handle NA values

Value

list of processed parameters

list of processed parameters

list of processed parameters
